ARDTool - A simple Automatic Rails Deployment Tool
==============================

This project' s purpose is to provide a simple helper tool for automatic, one-command deployment of Rails applications. It is tested with RVM to ensure no conflicts will occur. It is designed for deployment in Phusion Passenger-like environments, however you can always create your custom set of commands to run in a given place of the deployment script. It is written in C++.

Current version: v. 0.1
